{"word":"ἀποβιάζομαι","slug":"ἀποβιάζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποβιάζομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to force away</i>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be forced away</i> or <i>back</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to use force</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}